des:
How to use our skill:

For the best experience, please make sure to allow notifications on the skill in your Alexa app under device settings.

Get Started:
To Get Started: Say "Alexa, open ‘Brace Yourself Dental’”.

Request and Appointment
Say ‘schedule an appointment’ after Alexa completes the introduction to schedule a new appointment. 

You can also ask:
- What are your hours?
- What services do you provide?
- Are you running any promotions?
- What insurances do you accept?

We are constantly updating our skill to provide you with a world-class voice experience. 


You can reach us by phone at 718-220-8800

Give it a download and try it out!
